  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class RegistrationEvent
extends Registration
    This event is posted via the EventBus. Register on the EventBus for this event type to see the data that ExactTarget sends to their servers.

    Sent whenever a user registers or unregisters for push notifications with ExactTarget.
